com.microsoft.bingads.v10.bulk.entities

Class BidSuggestionData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.bingads.v10.bulk.entities.BidSuggestionData

  • public class BidSuggestionData
extends Object
    The best position, main line, and first page bid suggestion data corresponding to one keyword. If the requested SubmitDownloadParameters.getDataScope() includes BidSuggestionsData, the download will include bulk records corresponding to the properties of this class.
    See Also:
    BulkServiceManager, BulkOperation, BulkFileReader

    • Method Detail

      • getBestPosition

        public BulkKeywordBidSuggestion getBestPosition()
        Gets the best position bid.

        Represents a best position bid suggestion that is derived from BulkObject and can only be read from a bulk file by the BulkFileReader when reading the corresponding BulkKeyword. An instance of this class can represent a single best position bid, and thus one record in the bulk file. Properties of this class and of classes that it is derived from, correspond to fields of the Keyword Best Position Bid record in a bulk file.

        For more information, see Keyword Best Position Bid at http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=620266.
